@startuml Energy Grid

' | Stereotype | Meaning |
' |---|---|
' | `<<key>>` | Entities that are **directly read or compared** during the coordination decision — the agent must retrieve and reason about their properties to assign an EV to a charging slot |
' | `<<bridge>>` | The **cross-domain gap marker** — an entity that exists in one ontology but whose counterpart lives in the other; the semantic mapping the agent must negotiate |
' | `<<context>>` | Entities that provide **structural topology** — necessary to traverse the graph and locate the key entities, but not themselves decision variables |
' | `<<abstract>>` | **Base classes** from the CIM hierarchy — present only to satisfy inheritance chains; carry no scenario-specific semantics |

